: \"VSTest\"` to use the new platform instead.\n\nLet me work through the migration step by step and make sure everything compiles correctly.","outputTokens":987,"requestId":"082B:1F3FEB:87FF564:96A915D:69EACE10"},"id":"faee2636-93b1-4e9a-a8d9-23a64ed2467a","timestamp":"2026-04-24T01:57:59.591Z","parentId":"25296e23-8f9b-4002-b589-575b24c41b25"}
